{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01XEGbFQYuYG31RWFFoNRirV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01B8GWr3FPv69DjP7NUGeFiB","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create all config files","prompt":"I need you to create several configuration files for a Jakarta EE migration. Use the Write tool for each file. The base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nCreate these files:\n\n### 1. src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<persistence version=\"3.0\" xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence\"\n             xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n             xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_3_0.xsd\">\n    <persistence-unit name=\"petclinic\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n        <jta-data-source>java:jboss/datasources/ExampleDS</jta-data-source>\n        <properties>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.dialect\" value=\"org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.hbm2ddl.auto\" value=\"create-drop\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.show_sql\" value=\"true\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.format_sql\" value=\"true\"/>\n            <property name=\"jakarta.persistence.sql-load-script-source\" value=\"import.sql\"/>\n        </properties>\n    </persistence-unit>\n</persistence>\n```\n\n### 2. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<web-app xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n         xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n         version=\"6.0\">\n\n    <display-name>PetClinic Jakarta EE</display-name>\n\n    <welcome-file-list>\n        <welcome-file>index.jsp</welcome-file>\n    </welcome-file-list>\n\n    <!-- WebJars Servlet for serving webjars resources -->\n    <servlet>\n        <servlet-name>WebjarsServlet</servlet-name>\n        <servlet-class>org.webjars.servlet.WebjarsServlet</servlet-class>\n        <init-param>\n            <param-name>disableCache</param-name>\n            <param-value>false</param-value>\n        </init-param>\n        <load-on-startup>2</load-on-startup>\n    </servlet>\n    <servlet-mapping>\n        <servlet-name>WebjarsServlet</servlet-name>\n        <url-pattern>/webjars/*</url-pattern>\n    </servlet-mapping>\n\n    <jsp-config>\n        <jsp-property-group>\n            <url-pattern>*.jsp</url-pattern>\n            <page-encoding>UTF-8</page-encoding>\n        </jsp-property-group>\n    </jsp-config>\n</web-app>\n```\n\n### 3. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<beans xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/beans_4_0.xsd\"\n       bean-discovery-mode=\"all\"\n       version=\"4.0\">\n</beans>\n```\n\n### 4. configure-server.cli (in the project root directory)\nThis is a WildFly CLI script to configure the server:\n```\n# Configure the H2 datasource for development\n# The h2-default-datasource layer already provides ExampleDS\n# We just need to adjust some settings\n\n# Enable JPA SQL logging\n/subsystem=jpa:write-attribute(name=default-extended-persistence-inheritance,value=DEEP)\n\n# Set the context root to /\n/subsystem=undertow/server=default-server/host=default-host:write-attribute(name=default-web-module,value=ROOT.war)\n```\n\n### 5. src/main/webapp/index.jsp\nThis just redirects to the JAX-RS welcome page:\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%\n    response.sendRedirect(request.getContextPath() + \"/app/\");\n%>\n```\n\nCreate all 5 files using the Write tool.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":637,"cache_read_input_tokens":63302,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":637,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":7933},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"8f4de3b6-780f-4a18-bb9d-04e70d611ad1"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01XEGbFQYuYG31RWFFoNRirV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01AsBQk8HqmAKKygv6k7s6Fu","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create all JSP templates","prompt":"I'm migrating a Quarkus PetClinic app to standard Jakarta EE. I need to convert Qute templates to JSP files. The base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nCreate these JSP files using the Write tool. Note: The Qute `{msg:xxx}` syntax needs to be replaced with hardcoded English strings. The `{#for}` becomes `<c:forEach>`, `{#if}` becomes `<c:if>`, etc.\n\n### 1. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/base.jsp (layout tag file - actually we'll use includes)\n\nActually, since JSPs can't easily do Qute-style layout inheritance, I'll use a simpler approach with header/footer includes:\n\n### 1. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/header.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<!doctype html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>PetClinic :: a Jakarta EE Framework demonstration</title>\n  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/favicon.ico\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/css/petclinic.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\"><span></span></a>\n        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\" style>\n        <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n          <li class=\"active\">\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\" title=\"home page\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Home</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/find\" title=\"find owners\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Find Owners</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/vets.html\" title=\"veterinarians\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-th-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Veterinarians</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/oups\" title=\"trigger a RuntimeException to see how it is handled\">\n              <span class=\"fa exclamation-triangle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Error</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"container xd-container\">\n```\n\n### 2. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/footer.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### 3. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/welcome.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/pets.png\"/>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 4. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/error.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/pets.png\"/>\n        <h2>Error</h2>\n        <p>Something happened...</p>\n        <c:if test=\"${not empty message}\">\n          <p><c:out value=\"${message}\"/></p>\n        </c:if>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 5. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/vetList.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Veterinarians</h2>\n\n<table id=\"vets\" class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Name</th>\n            <th>Specialties</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <c:forEach var=\"vet\" items=\"${vets}\">\n        <tr>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${vet.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${vet.lastName}\"/></td>\n            <td>\n                <c:forEach var=\"s\" items=\"${vet.specialties}\">\n                <span><c:out value=\"${s.name}\"/>&nbsp;</span>\n                </c:forEach>\n                <c:if test=\"${vet.nrOfSpecialties == 0}\"><span>None</span></c:if>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        </c:forEach>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 6. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/findOwners.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Find Owners</h2>\n\n  <form action=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners\" method=\"get\"\n    class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"search-owner-form\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"control-group\" id=\"lastNameGroup\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" size=\"30\"\n            maxlength=\"80\" />\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors}\">\n            <span class=\"help-inline\">\n                <div>\n                    <c:forEach var=\"err\" items=\"${errors}\">\n                        <p><c:out value=\"${err}\"/></p>\n                    </c:forEach>\n                </div>\n            </span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Find Owner</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/new\">Add Owner</a>\n\n  </form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 7. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/ownerDetails.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"fmt\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.fmt\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owner Information</h2>\n\n    <table class=\"table table-striped\">\n      <tr>\n        <th>Name</th>\n        <td><b><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${owner.lastName}\"/></b></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Address</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.address}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>City</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.city}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Telephone</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.telephone}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/edit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Edit Owner</a>\n    <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/new\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Add New Pet</a>\n\n    <br /><br /><br />\n    <c:if test=\"${not empty owner.pets}\">\n    <h2>Pets and Visits</h2>\n\n    <table class=\"table table-striped\">\n      <c:forEach var=\"pet\" items=\"${owner.pets}\">\n      <tr>\n        <td valign=\"top\">\n          <dl class=\"dl-horizontal\">\n            <dt>Name</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></dd>\n            <dt>Birthdate</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.birthDate}\"/></dd>\n            <dt>Type</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.type.name}\"/></dd>\n          </dl>\n        </td>\n        <td valign=\"top\">\n          <table class=\"table-condensed\">\n            <thead>\n              <tr>\n                <th>Visit Date</th>\n                <th>Description</th>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td><a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/${pet.id}/edit\">Edit Pet</a></td>\n                <td><a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/${pet.id}/visits/new\">Add Visit</a></td>\n              </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <c:forEach var=\"visit\" items=\"${pet.sortedVisits}\">\n            <tr>\n              <td><c:out value=\"${visit.date}\"/></td>\n              <td><c:out value=\"${visit.description}\"/></td>\n            </tr>\n            </c:forEach>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      </c:forEach>\n    </table>\n    </c:if>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 8. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/ownersList.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owners</h2>\n\n<table id=\"owners\" class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"width: 150px;\">Name</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 200px;\">Address</th>\n            <th>City</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 120px\">Telephone</th>\n            <th>Pets</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <c:forEach var=\"owner\" items=\"${owners}\">\n        <tr>\n            <td>\n                <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}\"><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${owner.lastName}\"/></a>\n            </td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.address}\"/></td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.city}\"/></td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.telephone}\"/></td>\n            <td>\n                <c:forEach var=\"pet\" items=\"${owner.pets}\">\n                    <span><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></span>\n                </c:forEach>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        </c:forEach>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 9. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdateOwnerForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owner</h2>\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"add-owner-form\" method=\"post\">\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"firstName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Name</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"firstName\" name=\"firstName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.firstName}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['firstName']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['firstName']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"lastName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.lastName}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['lastName']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['lastName']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"address\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Address</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"address\" name=\"address\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.address}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['address']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['address']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"city\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">City</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"city\" name=\"city\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.city}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['city']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['city']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"telephone\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Telephone</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"telephone\" name=\"telephone\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.telephone}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['telephone']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['telephone']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">\n                <c:choose>\n                    <c:when test=\"${not empty owner}\">Edit Owner</c:when>\n                    <c:otherwise>Add Owner</c:otherwise>\n                </c:choose>\n            </button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 10. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdatePetForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>\n    <c:if test=\"${empty pet}\">New </c:if>\n    Pet\n</h2>\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" method=\"post\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"\" />\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n      <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Owner</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <span><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"name\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Name</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n            <div>\n                <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" value=\"<c:out value='${pet.name}' default=''/>\"/>\n            </div>\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['name']}\">\n                <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['name']}\"/></span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"birthDate\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Birthdate</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n            <div>\n                <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"YYYY-MM-DD\" title=\"Enter a date in this format: YYYY-MM-DD\" id=\"birthDate\" name=\"birthDate\" value=\"<c:out value='${pet.birthDate}' default=''/>\"/>\n            </div>\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['birthDate']}\">\n                <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['birthDate']}\"/></span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Type</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <select id=\"type\" name=\"type\">\n            <c:forEach var=\"petType\" items=\"${petTypes}\">\n            <option value=\"${petType.name}\" <c:if test=\"${not empty pet and not empty pet.type and petType.name == pet.type.name}\">selected</c:if>><c:out value=\"${petType.name}\"/></option>\n            </c:forEach>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">\n          <c:choose>\n            <c:when test=\"${not empty pet}\">Edit Pet</c:when>\n            <c:otherwise>Add Pet</c:otherwise>\n          </c:choose>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 11. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdateVisitForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>\n    <c:if test=\"${empty visit}\">New </c:if>\n    Visit\n</h2>\n\n<b>Pet</b>\n<table class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Name</th>\n            <th>Birthdate</th>\n            <th>Type</th>\n            <th>Owner</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tr>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.birthDate}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.type.name}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${pet.owner.lastName}\"/></td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" method=\"post\">\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"date\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Date</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n                        id=\"date\" name=\"date\" value=\"<c:out value='${visit.date}' default=''/>\"/>\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['date']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['date']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"description\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Description</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"description\" name=\"description\" value=\"<c:out value='${visit.description}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['description']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['description']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"petId\" value=\"1\" />\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">Add Visit</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n\n<br />\n<b>Previous Visits</b>\n<table class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>Date</th>\n        <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n    <c:if test=\"${not empty visit}\">\n    <c:forEach var=\"v\" items=\"${pet.sortedVisits}\">\n    <tr>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${v.date}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${v.description}\"/></td>\n    </tr>\n    </c:forEach>\n    </c:if>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\nPlease create ALL 11 files using the Write tool. The base path for all files is:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":637,"cache_read_input_tokens":63302,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":637,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":7933},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"8ce72f40-86af-43da-9178-39fe77c3a5e7"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to create several configuration files for a Jakarta EE migration. Use the Write tool for each file. The base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nCreate these files:\n\n### 1. src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<persistence version=\"3.0\" xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence\"\n             xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n             xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_3_0.xsd\">\n    <persistence-unit name=\"petclinic\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n        <jta-data-source>java:jboss/datasources/ExampleDS</jta-data-source>\n        <properties>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.dialect\" value=\"org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.hbm2ddl.auto\" value=\"create-drop\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.show_sql\" value=\"true\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.format_sql\" value=\"true\"/>\n            <property name=\"jakarta.persistence.sql-load-script-source\" value=\"import.sql\"/>\n        </properties>\n    </persistence-unit>\n</persistence>\n```\n\n### 2. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<web-app xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n         xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n         version=\"6.0\">\n\n    <display-name>PetClinic Jakarta EE</display-name>\n\n    <welcome-file-list>\n        <welcome-file>index.jsp</welcome-file>\n    </welcome-file-list>\n\n    <!-- WebJars Servlet for serving webjars resources -->\n    <servlet>\n        <servlet-name>WebjarsServlet</servlet-name>\n        <servlet-class>org.webjars.servlet.WebjarsServlet</servlet-class>\n        <init-param>\n            <param-name>disableCache</param-name>\n            <param-value>false</param-value>\n        </init-param>\n        <load-on-startup>2</load-on-startup>\n    </servlet>\n    <servlet-mapping>\n        <servlet-name>WebjarsServlet</servlet-name>\n        <url-pattern>/webjars/*</url-pattern>\n    </servlet-mapping>\n\n    <jsp-config>\n        <jsp-property-group>\n            <url-pattern>*.jsp</url-pattern>\n            <page-encoding>UTF-8</page-encoding>\n        </jsp-property-group>\n    </jsp-config>\n</web-app>\n```\n\n### 3. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<beans xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/beans_4_0.xsd\"\n       bean-discovery-mode=\"all\"\n       version=\"4.0\">\n</beans>\n```\n\n### 4. configure-server.cli (in the project root directory)\nThis is a WildFly CLI script to configure the server:\n```\n# Configure the H2 datasource for development\n# The h2-default-datasource layer already provides ExampleDS\n# We just need to adjust some settings\n\n# Enable JPA SQL logging\n/subsystem=jpa:write-attribute(name=default-extended-persistence-inheritance,value=DEEP)\n\n# Set the context root to /\n/subsystem=undertow/server=default-server/host=default-host:write-attribute(name=default-web-module,value=ROOT.war)\n```\n\n### 5. src/main/webapp/index.jsp\nThis just redirects to the JAX-RS welcome page:\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%\n    response.sendRedirect(request.getContextPath() + \"/app/\");\n%>\n```\n\nCreate all 5 files using the Write tool."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01B8GWr3FPv69DjP7NUGeFiB","session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"c766fabd-6f52-4670-b049-99516171b7f7"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm migrating a Quarkus PetClinic app to standard Jakarta EE. I need to convert Qute templates to JSP files. The base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output\n\nCreate these JSP files using the Write tool. Note: The Qute `{msg:xxx}` syntax needs to be replaced with hardcoded English strings. The `{#for}` becomes `<c:forEach>`, `{#if}` becomes `<c:if>`, etc.\n\n### 1. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/base.jsp (layout tag file - actually we'll use includes)\n\nActually, since JSPs can't easily do Qute-style layout inheritance, I'll use a simpler approach with header/footer includes:\n\n### 1. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/header.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<!doctype html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>PetClinic :: a Jakarta EE Framework demonstration</title>\n  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/favicon.ico\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/css/petclinic.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\"><span></span></a>\n        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\" style>\n        <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n          <li class=\"active\">\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\" title=\"home page\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Home</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/find\" title=\"find owners\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Find Owners</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/vets.html\" title=\"veterinarians\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-th-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Veterinarians</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/oups\" title=\"trigger a RuntimeException to see how it is handled\">\n              <span class=\"fa exclamation-triangle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Error</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"container xd-container\">\n```\n\n### 2. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/footer.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### 3. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/welcome.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/pets.png\"/>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 4. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/error.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/pets.png\"/>\n        <h2>Error</h2>\n        <p>Something happened...</p>\n        <c:if test=\"${not empty message}\">\n          <p><c:out value=\"${message}\"/></p>\n        </c:if>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 5. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/vetList.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Veterinarians</h2>\n\n<table id=\"vets\" class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Name</th>\n            <th>Specialties</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <c:forEach var=\"vet\" items=\"${vets}\">\n        <tr>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${vet.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${vet.lastName}\"/></td>\n            <td>\n                <c:forEach var=\"s\" items=\"${vet.specialties}\">\n                <span><c:out value=\"${s.name}\"/>&nbsp;</span>\n                </c:forEach>\n                <c:if test=\"${vet.nrOfSpecialties == 0}\"><span>None</span></c:if>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        </c:forEach>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 6. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/findOwners.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n  <h2>Find Owners</h2>\n\n  <form action=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners\" method=\"get\"\n    class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"search-owner-form\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"control-group\" id=\"lastNameGroup\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" size=\"30\"\n            maxlength=\"80\" />\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors}\">\n            <span class=\"help-inline\">\n                <div>\n                    <c:forEach var=\"err\" items=\"${errors}\">\n                        <p><c:out value=\"${err}\"/></p>\n                    </c:forEach>\n                </div>\n            </span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Find Owner</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/new\">Add Owner</a>\n\n  </form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 7. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/ownerDetails.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"fmt\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.fmt\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owner Information</h2>\n\n    <table class=\"table table-striped\">\n      <tr>\n        <th>Name</th>\n        <td><b><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${owner.lastName}\"/></b></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Address</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.address}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>City</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.city}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Telephone</th>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${owner.telephone}\"/></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/edit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Edit Owner</a>\n    <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/new\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Add New Pet</a>\n\n    <br /><br /><br />\n    <c:if test=\"${not empty owner.pets}\">\n    <h2>Pets and Visits</h2>\n\n    <table class=\"table table-striped\">\n      <c:forEach var=\"pet\" items=\"${owner.pets}\">\n      <tr>\n        <td valign=\"top\">\n          <dl class=\"dl-horizontal\">\n            <dt>Name</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></dd>\n            <dt>Birthdate</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.birthDate}\"/></dd>\n            <dt>Type</dt>\n            <dd><c:out value=\"${pet.type.name}\"/></dd>\n          </dl>\n        </td>\n        <td valign=\"top\">\n          <table class=\"table-condensed\">\n            <thead>\n              <tr>\n                <th>Visit Date</th>\n                <th>Description</th>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td><a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/${pet.id}/edit\">Edit Pet</a></td>\n                <td><a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}/pets/${pet.id}/visits/new\">Add Visit</a></td>\n              </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <c:forEach var=\"visit\" items=\"${pet.sortedVisits}\">\n            <tr>\n              <td><c:out value=\"${visit.date}\"/></td>\n              <td><c:out value=\"${visit.description}\"/></td>\n            </tr>\n            </c:forEach>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      </c:forEach>\n    </table>\n    </c:if>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 8. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/ownersList.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owners</h2>\n\n<table id=\"owners\" class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"width: 150px;\">Name</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 200px;\">Address</th>\n            <th>City</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 120px\">Telephone</th>\n            <th>Pets</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <c:forEach var=\"owner\" items=\"${owners}\">\n        <tr>\n            <td>\n                <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/${owner.id}\"><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${owner.lastName}\"/></a>\n            </td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.address}\"/></td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.city}\"/></td>\n            <td><c:out value=\"${owner.telephone}\"/></td>\n            <td>\n                <c:forEach var=\"pet\" items=\"${owner.pets}\">\n                    <span><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></span>\n                </c:forEach>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        </c:forEach>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 9. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdateOwnerForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>Owner</h2>\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"add-owner-form\" method=\"post\">\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"firstName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Name</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"firstName\" name=\"firstName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.firstName}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['firstName']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['firstName']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"lastName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.lastName}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['lastName']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['lastName']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"address\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Address</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"address\" name=\"address\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.address}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['address']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['address']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"city\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">City</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"city\" name=\"city\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.city}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['city']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['city']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"telephone\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Telephone</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"telephone\" name=\"telephone\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.telephone}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['telephone']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['telephone']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">\n                <c:choose>\n                    <c:when test=\"${not empty owner}\">Edit Owner</c:when>\n                    <c:otherwise>Add Owner</c:otherwise>\n                </c:choose>\n            </button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 10. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdatePetForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>\n    <c:if test=\"${empty pet}\">New </c:if>\n    Pet\n</h2>\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" method=\"post\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"\" />\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n      <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Owner</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <span><c:out value=\"${owner.firstName}\"/></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"name\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Name</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n            <div>\n                <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" value=\"<c:out value='${pet.name}' default=''/>\"/>\n            </div>\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['name']}\">\n                <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['name']}\"/></span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"birthDate\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Birthdate</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n            <div>\n                <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"YYYY-MM-DD\" title=\"Enter a date in this format: YYYY-MM-DD\" id=\"birthDate\" name=\"birthDate\" value=\"<c:out value='${pet.birthDate}' default=''/>\"/>\n            </div>\n            <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['birthDate']}\">\n                <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['birthDate']}\"/></span>\n            </c:if>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Type</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <select id=\"type\" name=\"type\">\n            <c:forEach var=\"petType\" items=\"${petTypes}\">\n            <option value=\"${petType.name}\" <c:if test=\"${not empty pet and not empty pet.type and petType.name == pet.type.name}\">selected</c:if>><c:out value=\"${petType.name}\"/></option>\n            </c:forEach>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">\n          <c:choose>\n            <c:when test=\"${not empty pet}\">Edit Pet</c:when>\n            <c:otherwise>Add Pet</c:otherwise>\n          </c:choose>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\n### 11. src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/createOrUpdateVisitForm.jsp\n```jsp\n<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n<h2>\n    <c:if test=\"${empty visit}\">New </c:if>\n    Visit\n</h2>\n\n<b>Pet</b>\n<table class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Name</th>\n            <th>Birthdate</th>\n            <th>Type</th>\n            <th>Owner</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tr>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.name}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.birthDate}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.type.name}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${pet.owner.firstName}\"/> <c:out value=\"${pet.owner.lastName}\"/></td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" method=\"post\">\n    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"date\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Date</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n                        id=\"date\" name=\"date\" value=\"<c:out value='${visit.date}' default=''/>\"/>\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['date']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['date']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"description\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Description</label>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n                <div>\n                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"description\" name=\"description\" value=\"<c:out value='${visit.description}' default=''/>\" />\n                </div>\n                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['description']}\">\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['description']}\"/></span>\n                </c:if>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"petId\" value=\"1\" />\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">Add Visit</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</form>\n\n<br />\n<b>Previous Visits</b>\n<table class=\"table table-striped\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>Date</th>\n        <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n    <c:if test=\"${not empty visit}\">\n    <c:forEach var=\"v\" items=\"${pet.sortedVisits}\">\n    <tr>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${v.date}\"/></td>\n        <td><c:out value=\"${v.description}\"/></td>\n    </tr>\n    </c:forEach>\n    </c:if>\n</table>\n<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n```\n\nPlease create ALL 11 files using the Write tool. The base path for all files is:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01AsBQk8HqmAKKygv6k7s6Fu","session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"d46bee24-885f-4b0b-b061-db05b90de9e3"}
