{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01B8GWr3FPv69DjP7NUGeFiB","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully created all 5 configuration files for the Jakarta EE migration. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n## Created Files\n\n### 1. **persistence.xml** \nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n\nThis file configures JPA 3.0 with:\n- Jakarta Persistence 3.0 namespace\n- JTA transaction type using WildFly's ExampleDS datasource\n- Hibernate H2 dialect for development\n- Automatic schema creation/drop\n- SQL logging enabled\n- Import script configured to load initial data\n\n### 2. **web.xml**\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml`\n\nThis file configures:\n- Jakarta EE Web Application 6.0\n- Welcome file pointing to index.jsp\n- WebjarsServlet for serving static assets from WebJars\n- JSP configuration with UTF-8 encoding\n\n### 3. **beans.xml**\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml`\n\nThis file enables:\n- Jakarta CDI 4.0\n- Bean discovery mode set to \"all\" for automatic CDI bean discovery\n\n### 4. **configure-server.cli**\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/configure-server.cli`\n\nWildFly CLI script that:\n- Configures JPA extended persistence inheritance\n- Sets the application context root to \"/\" by making it the default web module\n\n### 5. **index.jsp**\nLocation: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/index.jsp`\n\nSimple JSP that redirects to the JAX-RS application endpoint at `/app/`\n\nAll files have been created with the proper Jakarta EE namespaces and configurations for a modern Jakarta EE 10+ application running on WildFly."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"a0bcf5d8-04b3-4740-9b3d-e75d5ca1e231"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01Bdg3u1sFuJaZjT1rxC93Zf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01FGreGCXcXLLAYuyRyAjRm6","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/header.jsp","content":"<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n<!doctype html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>PetClinic :: a Jakarta EE Framework demonstration</title>\n  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/favicon.ico\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/css/petclinic.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\"><span></span></a>\n        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\" style>\n        <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n          <li class=\"active\">\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/\" title=\"home page\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Home</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/owners/find\" title=\"find owners\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Find Owners</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/vets.html\" title=\"veterinarians\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-th-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Veterinarians</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a href=\"${pageContext.request.contextPath}/app/oups\" title=\"trigger a RuntimeException to see how it is handled\">\n              <span class=\"fa exclamation-triangle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Error</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"container xd-container\">\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6809,"cache_read_input_tokens":11010,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6809,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":7231},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01AsBQk8HqmAKKygv6k7s6Fu","session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"358450d7-c005-4e47-8edd-aba2dae48fb1"}
