{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01AsBQk8HqmAKKygv6k7s6Fu","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully created all 11 JSP files for the Jakarta EE PetClinic migration. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n## Summary of JSP Files Created\n\nAll files were created in the directory:\n`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/jsp/`\n\n### Layout Files (using includes pattern):\n1. **header.jsp** - Contains the HTML head, navigation menu, and opening body/container tags\n2. **footer.jsp** - Contains the closing container/body tags and JavaScript includes\n\n### Page Files:\n3. **welcome.jsp** - Home page with pets image\n4. **error.jsp** - Error page displaying error messages\n5. **vetList.jsp** - List of veterinarians with their specialties\n6. **findOwners.jsp** - Owner search form\n7. **ownersList.jsp** - Table listing all owners with their details\n8. **ownerDetails.jsp** - Detailed view of an owner with their pets and visits\n9. **createOrUpdateOwnerForm.jsp** - Form for adding/editing owners\n10. **createOrUpdatePetForm.jsp** - Form for adding/editing pets\n11. **createOrUpdateVisitForm.jsp** - Form for adding visits to pets\n\n## Key Conversion Features:\n- Qute `{msg:xxx}` syntax replaced with hardcoded English strings\n- Qute `{#for}` loops converted to `<c:forEach>` JSTL tags\n- Qute `{#if}` conditionals converted to `<c:if>` JSTL tags\n- All expressions properly escaped using `<c:out>` for security\n- Jakarta Tags Core library used (`jakarta.tags.core`)\n- Proper JSP includes used instead of Qute's layout inheritance\n- Context path handling with `${pageContext.request.contextPath}`\n- Form validation error display using conditional error styling\n\nAll files follow standard JSP/JSTL patterns and are ready for use in a Jakarta EE application."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"8b755652-19db-421f-8e22-8be8ea539c95"}
