{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013sEUrdQUsQY5ncrDMQbiRY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The web search isn't working. Let me think about this differently. The core issue is that RESTEasy wraps the HttpServletRequest and Undertow's forward() won't accept it. \n\nThe best approach is to completely avoid JSP forwarding from JAX-RS and instead change the architecture. I'll create a `ViewServlet` that handles the JSP rendering, and have JAX-RS methods redirect to it, or I can use JAX-RS methods that return `StreamingOutput` to render the JSP. \n\nActually, the most pragmatic solution: Instead of forwarding from JAX-RS, I should use **plain Servlets** for the HTML-rendering endpoints. The JAX-RS endpoints that return JSON can stay as they are. Let me convert the HTML-rendering endpoints to Servlets.\n\nBut that would be a major refactor. Let me try a simpler approach first - use `include()` instead of `forward()`:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":562,"cache_read_input_tokens":115342,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":562,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":376},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"74a68cf0-caab-4a59-88be-0d4aafe6da2c"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013sEUrdQUsQY5ncrDMQbiRY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_019nuArvsnkJZ7yAP5r8C8oa","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"docker exec my_test_container_1 bash -c 'cat > /tmp/TestForward.java << '\\''EOF'\\''\nimport jakarta.servlet.*;\nimport jakarta.servlet.http.*;\nimport java.io.*;\n\npublic class TestForward {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        System.out.println(\"Testing include vs forward approach\");\n    }\n}\nEOF\necho \"done\"'","description":"Test approach"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":562,"cache_read_input_tokens":115342,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":562,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":376},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"978ceb6c-301c-4c8b-bd91-9e15ee7dc327"}
