{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017hAMxPH4NE8DAvS7uhdgwk","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<%@ page contentType=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\" language=\"java\" %>\n     2→<%@ taglib prefix=\"c\" uri=\"jakarta.tags.core\" %>\n     3→<jsp:include page=\"header.jsp\"/>\n     4→<h2>Owner</h2>\n     5→<form class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"add-owner-form\" method=\"post\">\n     6→    <div class=\"form-group has-feedback\">\n     7→\n     8→        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"firstName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n     9→            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Name</label>\n    10→            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n    11→                <div>\n    12→                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"firstName\" name=\"firstName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.firstName}' default=''/>\" />\n    13→                </div>\n    14→                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['firstName']}\">\n    15→                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['firstName']}\"/></span>\n    16→                </c:if>\n    17→            </div>\n    18→        </div>\n    19→\n    20→        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"lastName\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n    21→            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n    22→            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n    23→                <div>\n    24→                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.lastName}' default=''/>\" />\n    25→                </div>\n    26→                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['lastName']}\">\n    27→                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['lastName']}\"/></span>\n    28→                </c:if>\n    29→            </div>\n    30→        </div>\n    31→\n    32→        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"address\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n    33→            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Address</label>\n    34→            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n    35→                <div>\n    36→                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"address\" name=\"address\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.address}' default=''/>\" />\n    37→                </div>\n    38→                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['address']}\">\n    39→                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['address']}\"/></span>\n    40→                </c:if>\n    41→            </div>\n    42→        </div>\n    43→\n    44→        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"city\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n    45→            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">City</label>\n    46→            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n    47→                <div>\n    48→                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"city\" name=\"city\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.city}' default=''/>\" />\n    49→                </div>\n    50→                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['city']}\">\n    51→                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['city']}\"/></span>\n    52→                </c:if>\n    53→            </div>\n    54→        </div>\n    55→\n    56→        <div class=\"form-group <c:if test='${not empty errors[\"telephone\"]}'>has-error</c:if>\">\n    57→            <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Telephone</label>\n    58→            <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n    59→                <div>\n    60→                    <input class=\"form-control\" type=\"text\" id=\"telephone\" name=\"telephone\" value=\"<c:out value='${owner.telephone}' default=''/>\" />\n    61→                </div>\n    62→                <c:if test=\"${not empty errors['telephone']}\">\n    63→                    <span class=\"help-inline\"><c:out value=\"${errors['telephone']}\"/></span>\n    64→                </c:if>\n    65→            </div>\n    66→        </div>\n    67→\n    68→    </div>\n    69→    <div class=\"form-group\">\n    70→        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n    71→            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">\n    72→                <c:choose>\n    73→                    <c:when test=\"${not empty owner}\">Edit Owner</c:when>\n    74→                    <c:otherwise>Add Owner</c:otherwise>\n    75→                </c:choose>\n    76→            </button>\n    77→        </div>\n    78→    </div>\n    79→</form>\n    80→<jsp:include page=\"footer.jsp\"/>\n    81→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18927158-45c8-4480-8025-21200db12286","uuid":"9d1c163c-fdb2-4354-86ec-61846ea79dd2"}
